{"id":3047,"date":"2021-05-23T06:43:34","date_gmt":"2021-05-23T06:43:34","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/thescienceschool.edu.pk\/tsswp\/?page_id=3047"},"modified":"2021-06-09T11:10:43","modified_gmt":"2021-06-09T11:10:43","slug":"attendance","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/thescienceschool.edu.pk\/tsswp\/education\/parents-and-students\/attendance\/","title":{"rendered":"Attendance"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-page\" data-elementor-id=\"3047\" class=\"elementor elementor-3047\" data-elementor-settings=\"[]\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-section-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-967a0f0 elementor-section-full_width elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"967a0f0\" data-element_type=\"section\" id=\"edu_child_first_content\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-97ba54c\" data-id=\"97ba54c\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fe152cc elementor-widget elementor-widget-sidebar\" data-id=\"fe152cc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"sidebar.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<section id=\"nav_menu-3\" class=\"widget widget_nav_menu\"><div class=\"menu-parent-student-side-bar-container\"><ul id=\"menu-parent-student-side-bar\" class=\"menu\"><li id=\"menu-item-3072\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-3072\"><a href=\"https:\/\/thescienceschool.edu.pk\/tsswp\/education\/parents-and-students\/uniform\/\">Uniform<\/a><\/li>\n<li id=\"menu-item-3065\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-3065\"><a href=\"https:\/\/thescienceschool.edu.pk\/tsswp\/education\/parents-and-students\/medical-assistance\/\">Medical Assistance<\/a><\/li>\n<li id=\"menu-item-3063\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-3063\"><a href=\"https:\/\/thescienceschool.edu.pk\/tsswp\/education\/parents-and-students\/attendance\/\">Attendance<\/a><\/li>\n<li id=\"menu-item-3066\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-3066\"><a href=\"https:\/\/thescienceschool.edu.pk\/tsswp\/education\/parents-and-students\/report-to-student-and-parents\/\">Report to Student and Parents<\/a><\/li>\n<li id=\"menu-item-3069\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-3069\"><a href=\"https:\/\/thescienceschool.edu.pk\/tsswp\/education\/parents-and-students\/term-dates\/\">Term Dates<\/a><\/li>\n<li id=\"menu-item-3068\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-3068\"><a href=\"https:\/\/thescienceschool.edu.pk\/tsswp\/education\/parents-and-students\/security\/\">Security<\/a><\/li>\n<li id=\"menu-item-3070\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-3070\"><a href=\"https:\/\/thescienceschool.edu.pk\/tsswp\/education\/parents-and-students\/timings\/\">Timings<\/a><\/li>\n<li id=\"menu-item-3064\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-3064\"><a href=\"https:\/\/thescienceschool.edu.pk\/tsswp\/education\/parents-and-students\/catering\/\"><span id=\"Catering\">Catering<\/span><\/a><\/li>\n<li id=\"menu-item-3071\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-3071\"><a href=\"https:\/\/thescienceschool.edu.pk\/tsswp\/education\/parents-and-students\/transport\/\">Transport<\/a><\/li>\n<li id=\"menu-item-3067\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-3067\"><a href=\"https:\/\/thescienceschool.edu.pk\/tsswp\/education\/parents-and-students\/scholarships-and-commitments\/\">Scholarships and Commitments<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul><\/div><\/section>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-7c04ff7\" data-id=\"7c04ff7\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fddf00c elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"fddf00c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Attendance<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4f70a39 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"4f70a39\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><p>Regular and punctual attendance is essential. No student should be absent from school without permission in advance, except through illness. Attendance and punctuality information is recorded on reports and sent home at the end of each Term.<\/p><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-24fd472 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"24fd472\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Reporting Students Absence <\/h3>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5f797b8 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"5f797b8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><p>If students are unwell, parents are asked to call the School Office and leave a message, stating their name, their child\u2019s name and class\/section, the nature of the child\u2019s illness and when he\/she is expected to return.<\/p><p>When a student returns to school after illness, parents should authorize the absence by sending a signed application to the school. If they wish, parents can also send a signed note explaining their child\u2019s absence to the class teacher.<\/p><p>If a student is away for three days, parents are asked to contact the school. If illness is likely to be long, work may be set for the student to complete at home, which can be collected from the School Office.<\/p><p>Students should meet the teacher to discuss work that has been missed for follow up actions in tutorial sessions on return to school.<\/p><p><strong>Please note that absence may impact students\u2019 learning and progress.<\/strong><\/p><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8f79a21 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"8f79a21\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">MEDICAL APPOINTMENTS<\/h3>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ee35dd9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ee35dd9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><p>Wherever possible, medical appointments (doctor, dentist) should be made before or after school, or during school holidays.<\/p><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bfd8bca elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"bfd8bca\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Late Arrival<\/h3>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c3ef5e0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"c3ef5e0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><p>Students who arrive late (after 8.00 am) should report to the teacher on duty.<\/p><p>If a student is late for 3 consecutive days, he\/she will not be allowed to enter the school premises. A meeting will be set with the parents and they will be informed through text message or phone call.<\/p><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-93dac48 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"93dac48\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Holidays in Term Time<\/h3>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b3c6ef8 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"b3c6ef8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><p>A maximum of five days\u2019 absence is allowed for children to accompany their parents on an unavoidable holiday during term time, but only with the prior approval of the school. This approval will be subject to an otherwise strong record of attendance and punctuality. If a student\u2019s attendance is below the average of 93% for the previous term, requests are likely to be refused. Similarly, if a student is late to school or lessons for 5% or more of the time, any holiday requests are likely to be refused regardless of overall attendance.<\/p><p>Please do not book holidays until permission is granted. Absence for holidays is undesirable because it severely disrupts the student\u2019s programme of learning and assessment.<\/p><p>For all holidays, a formal application needs to be submitted to the School Office prior to proceeding on leave.<\/p><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Attendance Regular and punctual attendance is essential. No student should be absent from school without permission in advance, except through illness. Attendance and punctuality information is recorded on reports and sent home at the end of each Term. Reporting Students Absence If students are unwell, parents are asked to call the School Office and leave &hellip; <\/p>\n<div class=\"link-more\"><a href=\"https:\/\/thescienceschool.edu.pk\/tsswp\/education\/parents-and-students\/attendance\/\" class=\"more-link\">Read More<span class=\"screen-reader-text\"> &#8220;Attendance&#8221;<\/span><\/a><\/div>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":2815,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/thescienceschool.edu.pk\/tsswp\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/3047"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/thescienceschool.edu.pk\/tsswp\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/thescienceschool.edu.pk\/tsswp\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thescienceschool.edu.pk\/tsswp\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thescienceschool.edu.pk\/tsswp\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3047"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/thescienceschool.edu.pk\/tsswp\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/3047\/revisions"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thescienceschool.edu.pk\/tsswp\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/2815"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/thescienceschool.edu.pk\/tsswp\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=3047"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}